video.title: iZombie
video.synopsis: A medical student-turned-zombie tries to retain her humanity by eating brains at the morgue and finds she has an uncanny new gift for solving crimes.

episodes.synopsis: Once a doctor on the fast track, Liv Moore is now a zombie turned crime-solver who gets insights from eating the brains of murder victims.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: After eating the brain of a murdered artist, Liv absorbs traces of the victim's artistic passion. Later, the zombie who turned Liv asks for a favor.
episodes.title: Brother, Can You Spare a Brain?

episodes.synopsis: The hit-and-run death of a mild-mannered suburban dad takes a surprising turn. Liv grapples with human feelings for Major.
episodes.title: The Exterminator

episodes.synopsis: A new case involving a brutal gang murder puts suspicions about Clive's past into Liv's head. Major finally makes a decision on his new roommate.
episodes.title: Liv and Let Clive

episodes.synopsis: Liv's new acceptance of her life as a zombie hits the rails when she has to eat the brain of an extreme sports fanatic who was an old friend.
episodes.title: Flight of the Living Dead

episodes.synopsis: Ravi cheers Liv on when a dead hacker's brains turn her into an obsessed gamer. But things get complicated when an unexpected guest comes to call.
episodes.title: Virtual Reality Bites

episodes.synopsis: As Seattle's zombie plague continues, Liv and Clive investigate the death of a pregnant woman whose brains bring out Liv's maternal instincts.
episodes.title: Maternity Liv

episodes.synopsis: The murder of a radio show host who doled out relationship advice has Liv digesting some new insights about everyone's feelings.
episodes.title: Dead Air

episodes.synopsis: While Blaine and Major continue to circle each other, Liv and Clive's newest investigation places them in a game of paintball that could turn deadly.
episodes.title: Patriot Brains

episodes.synopsis: Liv and Major both have trouble coping with recent events, while Clive and Liv investigate a case linking psychotic episodes to a new energy drink.
episodes.title: Mr. Berserk

episodes.synopsis: A suspicious suicide puts Clive and Liv on a case involving Major. When Liv is able to eat the victim's brains, a strange paranoia comes into play.
episodes.title: Astroburger

episodes.synopsis: Liv thinks like a high-schooler to solve the murder of a drunken teenager. Later, she makes a shocking discovery about Sebastian.
episodes.title: Dead Rat, Live Rat, Brown Rat, White Rat

episodes.synopsis: While Ravi continues working on his cure, some old cases come back into focus for Liv and Clive ... and another one could leave Major in the cold.
episodes.title: Blaine's World

episodes.synopsis: Liv eats the brains of a grumpy old man, Ravi and Major discover a curious side effect of the zombie cure, and Blaine moves his business to new digs.
episodes.title: Grumpy Old Liv

episodes.synopsis: Clive and Liv look into the murder of a fraternity brother, Ravi and Major try to score some utopium, and Blaine schemes to expand his drug trade.
episodes.title: Zombie Bro

episodes.synopsis: Liv learns that a trophy wife pushed to her death has some startling secrets, and Peyton returns to lead a task force combating the utopium trade.
episodes.title: Real Dead Housewife of Seattle

episodes.synopsis: Liv goes country after eating the brains of an aspiring singer, and Blaine goes after the thug who tainted the utopium at the boat party.
episodes.title: Even Cowgirls Get the Black and Blues

episodes.synopsis: While Blaine and Ravi use newly cut utopium to search for a cure, Liv eats the brains of a youth basketball coach to track down his killer.
episodes.title: Love & Basketball

episodes.synopsis: Liv becomes a gambling junkie after eating a lawyer's brains, and Major discovers the FBI is on the trail of Vaughn's illicit Max Rager activities.
episodes.title: Max Wager

episodes.synopsis: Liv turns goth after she consumes the brains of a morbid magician, and Blaine asks Liv to help him find out who has been killing the zombies.
episodes.title: Abra Cadaver

episodes.synopsis: Clive comes under suspicion when his stalker ex-girlfriend is killed, and Liv gets more than a little jealous herself after eating the woman's brains.
episodes.title: The Hurt Stalker

episodes.synopsis: The brains of a self-styled "superhero" vigilante turn Liv into a caped avenger, and Blaine gets closer to discovering how the utopium got tainted.
episodes.title: Cape Town

episodes.synopsis: Clive and Liv look into a murder on the set of a zombie-themed TV show, and Ravi reveals to Liv and Major that the zombie cure is only temporary.
episodes.title: Method Head

episodes.synopsis: A librarian who secretly writes sexy fiction turns up poisoned, Dale and Peyton tangle over Blaine's fate, and Liv and Drake get busy.
episodes.title: Fifty Shades of Grey Matter

episodes.synopsis: Three decapitated bodies wash ashore, leaving Liv no brains to eat for clues. Meanwhile, Peyton's boss goes missing, and a utopium turf war escalates.
episodes.title: Physician, Heal Thy Selfie

episodes.synopsis: Liv eats the brains of a pathological liar to uncover the truth about the utopium couriers buried in the field, and Blaine discovers Major's secret.
episodes.title: The Whopper

episodes.synopsis: It's all sunshine and rainbows for Liv after she eats the brains of a cheery coffee shop owner, and Mr. Boss settles an old score with Blaine.
episodes.title: Eternal Sunshine of the Caffeinated Mind

episodes.synopsis: Clive and Liv look into the slaying of a scientist connected to Vaughn and Max Rager, and Blaine faces a tough choice when he turns to Ravi for help.
episodes.title: He Blinded Me... with Science

episodes.synopsis: Reluctantly, Liv eats the brains of a stripper to help Peyton's case against Mr. Boss, and Ravi discovers the new cure has unexpected side effects.
episodes.title: Pour Some Sugar, Zombie

episodes.synopsis: Liv gets her pre-zombie personality back after eating the brains of a super-competitive student, and Major and Ravi scheme against Vaughn.
episodes.title: Reflections of the Way Liv Used to Be

episodes.synopsis: When they find themselves fresh out of brains, Liv and Ravi turn to Blaine for help. Meanwhile, the FBI arrests Major for the Chaos Killings.
episodes.title: Dead Beat

episodes.synopsis: While Vaughn parties to celebrate selling Max Rager to mercenaries, Liv, Clive and Major move in to free Drake and other captive zombies.
episodes.title: Salivation Army

episodes.synopsis: In the aftermath of the Max Rager massacre, Liv investigates Vivian's plan to turn Seattle into a zombie homeland, and Ravi works to improve the cure.
episodes.title: Heaven Just Got a Little Bit Smoother

episodes.synopsis: Liv and Major butt heads after eating the brains of a moody teen and her dorky father, and Clive faces questions about his slain young friend Wally.
episodes.title: Zombie Knows Best

episodes.synopsis: Blissed out on a guru's brains, Liv joins Clive to solve his murder. Ravi tries to mend fences with Peyton, and Major's time runs short.
episodes.title: Eat, Pray, Liv

episodes.synopsis: Clive investigates the murder of an office worker whose brains turn Liv into a shameless gossip. Major braves danger in his quest to find Natalie.
episodes.title: Wag the Tongue Slowly

episodes.synopsis: The brains of a dominatrix turn Liv into a domineering "bad cop" as she and Clive look for a suspicious peeping Tom. Major faces a wrenching choice.
episodes.title: Spanking the Zombie

episodes.synopsis: Liv morphs into a flighty, manipulative drama queen while searching for a nightclub DJ's killer. Blaine reveals a dramatic secret about the cure.
episodes.title: Some Like It Hot Mess

episodes.synopsis: Liv becomes a cheery optimist while investigating the murder of a sweet but philandering preschool teacher. Blaine faces a reckoning with his past.
episodes.title: Dirt Nap Time

episodes.synopsis: The brains of an obnoxious internet prankster lead Liv and Clive into a twisted tale of murder. Ravi must infiltrate a group of anti-zombie zealots.
episodes.title: Eat a Knievel

episodes.synopsis: The geeked-out brains of a role-playing game fanatic send Liv on a quest to find a killer. Ravi tries to stall the plans of zombie-hating crusaders.
episodes.title: Twenty-Sided, Die

episodes.synopsis: Suffering visions of her dead ex, Liv helps Peyton with a tangled case of suicide and murder. Ravi schemes to rescue Don E. from the zombie hunters.
episodes.title: Return of the Dead Guy

episodes.synopsis: After a deadly standoff, Liv and Clive race to track down the zombie hunters' leader. Peyton follows a lead deeper into a conspiracy.
episodes.title: Conspiracy Weary

episodes.synopsis: Liv gets flirty on the brains of a promiscuous doctor conducting a mysterious investigation. Chief zombie-hater Harley Johns gives everyone a shock.
episodes.title: Looking for Mr. Goodbrain, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Trouble brews at Fillmore-Graves as Discovery Day draws nigh, and Liv uncovers the grim conspiracy behind the deadly flu outbreak.
episodes.title: Looking for Mr. Goodbrain, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: With Seattle now a militarized zombie quarantine zone, Liv investigates the grisly death of a rabid football fan killed in a brains-processing plant.
episodes.title: Are You Ready for Some Zombies?

episodes.synopsis: The brains of a socialite murdered with a golf ball turn Liv into an insufferable bore. Meanwhile, a violent zombie prophet gains a cult following.
episodes.title: Blue Bloody

episodes.synopsis: The death of a hopeless romantic killed while being smuggled into Seattle puts Liv and Clive on the trail of a ruthless brains black marketeer.
episodes.title: Brainless in Seattle, Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Liv and Clive use Ravi as bait in a plan to flush out the human smuggler. Hunting for an explosive video, Major's team runs afoul of the zombie cult.
episodes.title: Brainless in Seattle, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Liv channels a scrappy hockey player as she and Clive investigate a multiple zombiecide. A brains shortage propels Fillmore-Graves to drastic action.
episodes.title: Goonstruck

episodes.synopsis: A pretentious actress's brains help Liv when she goes underground to keep Mama Leone's smuggling network alive. Ravi takes a big risk to help Peyton.
episodes.title: My Really Fair Lady

episodes.synopsis: Eating the brain of a "professional wingman" turns Liv into a playboy who goes out on the town with Clive and Ravi. Major is given an important task.
episodes.title: Don't Hate the Player, Hate the Brain

episodes.synopsis: After she consumes the brains of a slain live-action role-playing knight, Liv helps Clive uncover dark secrets among a group of zombie LARPers.
episodes.title: Chivalry Is Dead

episodes.synopsis: Fillmore-Graves locks down Seattle to catch a serial zombie-killer, Blaine targets the mayor, and Liv, Peyton and Ravi clash over the fate of Isobel.
episodes.title: Mac-Liv-Moore

episodes.synopsis: While Ravi studies Isobel's condition, Fillmore-Graves interrogates one of Liv's coyotes. Brother Love tries to bring Blaine into the fold.
episodes.title: Yipee Ki Brain, Motherscratcher

episodes.synopsis: Major's undercover sting takes an unexpected turn. Brother Love stokes the fires of zombie rage. Liv takes action as Isobel's condition worsens.
episodes.title: Insane in the Germ Brain

episodes.synopsis: While Major whisks Liv out of Seattle for her own protection, Ravi eats the brains of a narcissist to help Clive investigate Brother Love for murder.
episodes.title: You've Got to Hide Your Liv Away

episodes.synopsis: The outside world further isolates Seattle while Peyton, Ravi, Clive and Major race to save Liv from execution for her work as Renegade.
episodes.title: And He Shall Be a Good Man

episodes.synopsis: Tensions in Seattle skyrocket after zombie-on-human violence exacerbates a brains shortage. Ravi warns a colleague about the downside of a cure.
episodes.title: Thug Death

episodes.synopsis: Jazzed on fitness guru brains, Liv helps Clive with the convenience store case. Peyton tangles with city council over a zombie-positive PR campaign.
episodes.title: Dead Lift

episodes.synopsis: Ravi panics when he and Liv go undercover at a dance competition to solve a murder-by-poison. Anti-zombie fervor grips a junior high school.
episodes.title: Five, Six,	Seven, Ate!

episodes.synopsis: Liv and Clive follow a twisty tech trail to investigate a visionary entrepreneur's murder. Blaine tries to charm his way into a journalist's favor.
episodes.title: Dot	Zom

episodes.synopsis: While Al wraps up her explosive story, Blaine falls under suspicion for killing his swaggering teenage neighbor. Major suffers mysterious memory loss.
episodes.title: Death Moves	 Pretty Fast

episodes.synopsis: Major scrambles to source more brains when Seattle's supply runs critically short. Scandalous publicity takes down Blaine -- but not for long.
episodes.title: The	Scratchmaker

episodes.synopsis: The brains of a sharp-tongued top chef help Liv and Clive corner a killer. A lethal attack sends Major hunting for a mole inside Fillmore-Graves.
episodes.title: Filleted to Rest

episodes.synopsis: Amped up on the brains of a slithery salesman, Liv and Ravi compete to solve a murder. Major tries to convince top Washington brass to spare Seattle.
episodes.title: Death of	a Car Salesman

episodes.synopsis: Flashbacks to the '90s help Liv and Clive with a teen beauty contest murder case. Ravi and Peyton track down clues to the original tainted Utopium.
episodes.title: The	Fresh Princess

episodes.synopsis: In a city on the edge, the brains of a popped P.I. turn Liv into a hardboiled gumshoe tracking down a pinched dose of zombie cure worth killing for.
episodes.title: Night and the Zombie City

episodes.synopsis: Ravi uses Major as "gigolo bait" in his hunt for the missing kids, and Liv brings the glam searching for the killer of a flamboyant drag queen.
episodes.title: Killer Queen

episodes.synopsis: While Major faces a changing of the tide in Seattle, Liv, Clive and Ravi undertake a mission impossible in Atlanta to retrieve the final zombie cure.
episodes.title: Bye,	Zombies

episodes.synopsis: As Liv, Ravi and Clive race to finalize the cure, Peyton faces a showdown with Blaine, and Major takes a bold gamble to save Seattle once and for all.
episodes.title: All's	Well That Ends Well
